The paper deals with signal recovery from incomplete measurements, which is a common problem in signal processing and image analysis. The use of total variation minimization and analysis l1-recovery techniques suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of information theory (cs.IT), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), signal processing (cs.SP), or numerical analysis (cs.NA).
